--- Switchblade ---

Switchblade smiles as he relaxes in the chair, "Probably... 
Motormaster, would you like to explain what you were doing there, 
molesting the console like that!" Switchblade's smile widdens even 
more as he peers up at the tell bot.


On 4 Jun 2001, at 19:27, robertdahl wrote:

> "We have a spy working right now, on checking when the Autobots leave,
> you will follow them. But first, we have some more troops to obtain."
> One of the council Members says.
> 
> Slugslinger and Apeface move back from the angered Havotron, but
> Spinister dosent seem disturbed. 
> 
> "Come now, there is no need for this Havotron" one of the Council
> members adds. ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
> Motormaster turns and growls at Switchblade, cruel intentions flaring
> in his eyes, "I'll feed you to the Terrorcons you little.." He is
> caught off guard by a swing from Megatron, "You will do nothing to
> him." Megatron turns his attention. "But I am sure he had a good
> reason Switchblade. Motormaster is gruff, but not unstable like the
> other Stunticons."
